title: The Real People
description:
The Real People

"The Joys of Losing Weight"

Pre-Beirut Zach Condon project.  Unfortunately I don&#039;t know much else about this recording.  From what I&#039;ve read I assume Condon recorded all the tracks on his own.  Don&#039;t know when said recording took place though.  One can hear some of the style that later becomes evident in Beirut, yet these songs are vastly different. 

All tracks untitled.

Any further info or other pre-Beirut recordings would be highly appreciated.

Enjoy!
